data.description: CALLING ALL INVESTORS!! You will fall in love with this beautiful home in Dequeen Addition neighborhood. Home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths & open concepts for the living room, kitchen & dining area, great for entertaining. This home has granite throughout, inside utility room & large closet space. Has nearby shopping, entertainment, golf course & an easy access to US-96. Why wouldn't you want to live here? This house has everything. Great space for backyard & even side yard to allow your imagination to bring an outdoor space to be your personal outdoor getaway.
